Class KmlCoord

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject

          com.nitrous.gwt.earth.client.api.KmlCoord

public class KmlCoord
extends KmlObjectBase

A single tuple consisting of floating point values for longitude, latitude, and altitude (in that order). Longitude and latitude values are in degrees. 

 
  • longitude = -180 and <= 180
    •  
 
  • latitude = -90 and = 90
    •  
 
  • altitude values (optional) are in meters above sea level
    •
